      "recording_attendee_id": "a1ef82a0-f5b6-490c-87a0-c70471d34508",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "I'm great. How are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "cd5d1bda-1055-44af-8613-cec1ee4cc026",
      "recording_id": "9a715a70-7e0a-4d98-9d3b-384b3b286c8e",
      "end_time": 79.77,
      "start_time": 44.13,
      "recording_attendee_id": "79b565ac-2665-4009-9907-9da73819b65c",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "I'm good, I'm good. Hey I caught your out of office uh last week um notice that you were gonna be returning this week and wanted to follow up with a phone call? Um We are an internet listing service with an exclusive partnership with facebook marketplace. Um the email that I sent you was budgeting for twenty-one let's connect and just wanted to see how things are going for you in regards to your budgeting and if you had plans to bring on any additional um support would love to set up a ten to fifteen minute call to to talk to you more about a photo and what we're what we got going on over here?"
